item.description:
Over and over, I read that "Nothing is more important than feeling good."  Makes sense to me, since ultimately this is the reason that you want anything.  Right?  And, this is why we chose "good vibrations" or feeling good as the focus of our meetup group.

Feeling good is also the vibrational means to get the "things" that you want!  So that's cool.

So join us in this evening as we all share and play with some of our favorite strategies for amping up our feeling good state.

Imagine how good you're going to feel by the end of this night as we do one feeling good process after another!

Please remember, when you RSVP "yes", we expect you, prepare for you, and look forward to you being with us!  If your plans change, please be considerate of us as your hosts, and let us know by changing your RSVP or e-mailing Ann at annide@newpossibilitiescoaching.com.  Most of you have been really good about this lately, and we really appreciate it!  Thank you!

Eagerly looking forward to feeling good with you!

Ann and Mark
item.how_to_find_us: We're down a long driveway. Look for white mailbox with our name and #276, across from large, old, white house. Please park as efficiently as possible if in driveway! Parking also close by on Garvey Road. Park on even numbered side of street.

item.name: Strategies for feeling GOOD!
